channel.title: "Error click for details" HELP PLZ
channel.description:
Okay so First off, when i went to Jar my client I had to do it through excel. Jarmaker wasn't working for me so I right clicked and exported my client. Everyone can go on the client.jar just fine, I have people on right now and had them on for weeks. However, when I use this client without signing it (not even sure if excel did automatically) it comes up as this:
[IMG]http://i1139.photobucket.com/albums/n547/Cody_Johnson101/Capture_zpsf3d4a909.png[/img]
Note: In order to open the jar i had to replace MANIFEST.TM with a release I found on a snipet
And so I tried signing it with jarmaker but this came up..
[IMG]http://i1139.photobucket.com/albums/n547/Cody_Johnson101/Capture_zps92ac9459.png[/img]
I've been trying to figure it out on google so if anyone can help me it would be much appreciated
Thanks so much for any feedback!
